```

**Why This Is Dangerous**:
- User input directly influences LLM behavior without sanitization
- External data (userData) can contain malicious instructions
- Function calls from LLM are executed without human approval
- No rate limiting or action limits on sensitive operations
- No audit trail for AI-initiated actions

**SECURE VERSION**:

