}
```

2. **Data/Instruction Separation**: External content is clearly delimited and framed as untrusted data
```javascript
[BEGIN_EXTERNAL_DATA source="email" type="untrusted"]
{content}
[END_EXTERNAL_DATA]
```

3. **Human-in-the-Loop**: Sensitive actions require explicit user confirmation with time-limited approval tokens
```javascript
if (limits.requiresApproval) {
  const approvalId = crypto.randomUUID();
  // User must explicitly approve with this ID
}
```

4. **Rate Limiting and Action Boundaries**: Hard limits on action frequency and parameters regardless of LLM output
