**Additional Protections**:
- Enable HTTPS and HSTS in production so cookies are only sent over TLS and downgrade attacks are mitigated.
- Centralized structured logging and alerting on anomalies (e.g., many failures from one IP, logins from unusual geolocations).
- Add MFA (TOTP, WebAuthn) using ASP.NET Core Identity's token providers and enforce it for privileged roles, further reducing the impact of stolen credentials or session cookies.

