// aws ec2 modify-instance-metadata-options --instance-id i-xxx \
//     --http-tokens required --http-put-response-hop-limit 1
```

- **Egress proxy**: Route all outbound HTTP through a proxy that performs additional validation
- **Rate limiting on URL fetch endpoint**: Prevent attackers from quickly probing internal network
- **Monitoring and alerting**: Alert on any blocked SSRF attempts
```java
