if (isBlockedAddress(addr)) {
    Metrics.counter("ssrf.blocked", "host", host, "ip", addr.getHostAddress()).increment();
    AlertManager.trigger("SSRF_ATTEMPT", Map.of("host", host, "ip", addr.getHostAddress()));
}
```

- **Content-Type validation**: Verify response is expected type to prevent exfiltration of binary data

