```

**Why This Is Vulnerable**:
1. `new Template()` with user string compiles arbitrary code
2. FreeMarker has powerful built-ins like `?new` (ObjectConstructor)
3. Can instantiate arbitrary Java classes

**Attack Example**:
```freemarker
