2. **Component-by-Component Validation**:
```java
// Never trust combined paths - validate each piece
for (String component : pathComponents) {
    if (!SAFE_PATH_COMPONENT.matcher(component).matches()) {
        // Rejects: "..", ".", empty, encoded sequences, special chars
        response.sendError(HttpServletResponse.SC_BAD_REQUEST);
        return;
